  "notes": "Captured 2026-04 Shopify behavior for `metafieldDefinitionUpdate(definition: { pin })`: `pin: true` pins an unpinned product definition, `pin: false` unpins a pinned definition, constrained update pin returns the same `UNSUPPORTED_PINNING` user error shape as pinning, and owner-type pin-cap rejection returns `PINNED_LIMIT_REACHED`. The capture temporarily unpins existing product definitions, creates disposable product-owned definitions in a temporary namespace, deletes them, and restores original pins."
